    "claudePromptTopicsEnd": "\n\nExamples of good categories: \"World War II\", \"Shakespeare's Plays\", \"Human Body Systems\", \"Solar System\", \"American Civil Rights Movement\"\n\nRespond with ONLY a valid JSON array of 10 topic strings appropriate for high school level education.\n\nDo not include any other text in your response. Please respond in ",
