    "claudePromptGameEnd": "\n\nGenerate exactly 5 TRUE statements and 2 FALSE statements about this topic:\n- The 5 true statements should be factual, accurate, and cover different aspects of the topic\n- The 2 false statements should be plausible but incorrect \"hallucinations\"\n- Adjust complexity based on difficulty level\n- Make sure facts are diverse and cover different subtopics\n\nMake the false statements believable but clearly wrong to an expert. Ensure all statements are interesting and educational. Focus on different aspects or details of the topic to ensure variety.\n\nRespond with ONLY a valid JSON object in this exact format:\n{\n  \"true_statements\": [\"true statement 1\", \"true statement 2\", \"true statement 3\", \"true statement 4\", \"true statement 5\"],\n  \"false_statements\": [\"false statement 1\", \"false statement 2\"],\n  \"explanations\": [\"explanation for false statement 1\", \"explanation for false statement 2\"]\n}\n\nThe explanations array should contain brief explanations of why each corresponding false statement is incorrect and what the truth actually is.\n\nDo not include any other text. Please respond in ",
